{"tid":1682391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有6日就到全民口罩日！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-30T04:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T12:31:36.000Z","uid":27026,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb2233a1e0f6ee7e1c7a056dc945c17440e9a29","tid":1682391,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:26:34.000Z","msg":"為咗宣傳11.5全民口罩日，我會每日都會開一個po倒數同提醒大家果日戴口罩，務求令到果日我要見到個個戴晒口罩返工返學放工放學！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本戴開嘅就繼續戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以做嘅野就係手人置頂呢個po，打個「推」、push、貼文宣圖等等，再身體力行啲嘅可以share埋出公海，同時我會收集呢個po嘅文宣圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11.5 全民口罩日！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdLPVic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdLPVic.jpg&h=46afe79c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nh0sGYd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnh0sGYd.jpg&h=c3d72001&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zzhjKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zzhjKU.jpg&h=b8a0aa27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAr3ZKV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAr3ZKV.jpg&h=1343fb1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PtgPaRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPtgPaRB.jpg&h=25b5f2da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPi9Vih.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPi9Vih.jpg&h=383643cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ax04KbD.jpg\" data-t